{"tid":240970,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【泰劇】討論區","createTime":"2017-05-12T19:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T17:13:05.000Z","uid":9684,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc300ec950b0c561f698f9529b9edc7af957887c","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:34:29.000Z","msg":"LIHKG有無泰劇同好？？<br />\n初初睇GMM TV嗰啲 比較後生 活潑啲 節奏比較快 一集8個字左右 <br />\n<br />\n出名啲又易入口:荷爾蒙，有3季 都係校園片啦，不外乎爭仔爭女，不過比傳統校園片 多咗BL GL師生戀咁。都幾舊2013年出既，我自己都無睇到第3季 <br />\n第3季走咗好多舊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話:其中一女角Punpun真人畀人踢爆過食冰有埋圖，佢個有錢老豆出面話因為想減肥誤信朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後又試過係instagram Post另一個女星係八婆話人搶佢男朋友，但Punpun呢個人仲係泰國好紅，依家仲有套佢做女主角既戲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有錢就是任性。<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他網上評語都幾好，又容易搵到中字睇既<br />\nBL:一年生<br />\n新過荷爾蒙，不過都播完一段時間。男主角singto幾靚仔既，但無乜心機睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> fb都好多人讚。<br />\n<br />\n搞笑: I wanna be a sup'star 我要成為超級大明星<br />\n女主角gypso男主角Push 兩個個樣第一眼都係奇奇怪怪，但睇睇下就順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 故事就係個男係大明星，女既想做大明星 機緣巧合同居 然後一齊 劇情係娘既 但幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話:女主角Gypso係高材生，泰國最高學府朱拉隆功大學畢業，首主題曲係佢第一次唱 好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PGfPNuFMNfg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPGfPNuFMNfg&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=3ae5f07b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PGfPNuFMNfg</a><br />\n佢家姐Gypsy都整過個嘴，都幾奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都有做戲，配角多。男主角Push係中國勁紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國fans叫佢推哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲播緊:Water boyy<br />\n呢套早幾年有出電影版，中譯好似係 水漾青春。Youtube有中字預告，好大膽😂依家電視劇播到第5集，男主角嗰班好似成日唔著衫咁。簡單啲咁講個劇情就係泳隊隊長男主角同佢教練爸爸嘈咗，咁啱泳隊有新人同男主角做rmmate，之後日久生情咁。幾激動既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第4集已經有床戲<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多播完評語都幾好，bilibili都會有:單身公寓、真愛就親親、醜小鴨、丘比特的眼淚（呢套好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇咗第一集feel到幾膠下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好被佢啲娘到喊既情節嚇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）u prince<br />\n<br />\n有啲我無睇，但都幾hit既:娘娘腔日記、love sick⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n好多好多 各位有睇既補充補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上都係比較節奏明快，啱睇開韓劇日劇歐美劇。"},{"pid":"6900d30891403b933ab8c42718749b0be826ff79","tid":240970,"uid":43849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:39:04.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef51a0efcbe02eea31edc66deef9c1429050ed1","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T20:16:35.000Z","msg":"GMM TV都係啲新啲既電視台<br />\n傳統泰國電視台啲泰劇都好娘，係好撚娘！<br />\nch3 ch7呢2個都應該係大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 煲泰劇閱歷少，望大家指教指教。<br />\n佢地出嗰啲戲，其實唔係好分到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排睇ch3多，結論係 好清水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錫錫都係額頭、面豬登同手，極少真係嚟真錫嘴。某程度你可以當係彩色播放既粵語長片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱煲完 名門紳士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  2013年出 台慶劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講5個少爺，唔同阿媽生 細細個老豆同3個阿媽就過咗生，由2個嫲嫲湊大。因為死咗老豆同個frd約好咗 兩家人既小朋友有婚約，但係老豆個frd嗰家人都好貪慕虛榮，5個少爺都唔想娶閪女人，故仔就圍繞5個少爺搵到真愛既過程。<br />\n<br />\n睇我名都知我係二少夫婦既fans，不過當少我係為咗3少 James jirayu睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三少instagram真係好丁得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三少都好睇，三少奶奶直情係成個系列最好睇既少奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇開cctvb日韓劇既，你會覺得成套戲拖嚟做，一集1.45hr 真係好長氣，我中意二少個故仔我都要飛住睇。不過真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 二少夫婦都好襯，但二少奶奶已經有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩ff都無曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 二少奶奶早排套fanday 一日情人 有係香港上 係毒撚悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都好睇 二少奶奶都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個禮拜ch3個演唱會，二少夫婦都好情侶檔出場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rUdRl_-BMFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrUdRl_-BMFw&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=aafc9a77\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rUdRl_-BMFw</a><br />\n不過好無聽就⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇埋其他，更加覺得點解咁都可以出嚟唱，仲要勁快無飛買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有追開ch3既劇，知道邊對係真情侶，邊對係做出嚟會投入好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有樣值得一提係泰國人打扮造型真係好厲害，成個show又唱又跳，佢地係幾分鐘內就可以轉造型真係好佩服，係成個髮型唔同咗但又唔亂，衫又換埋唔係加衫減衫係成套唔同咗，佢地女既著得好sexy又low cut又露背都仲夾到gap 又可以走嚟走去 真係厲害厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uhpX9TWzNZs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuhpX9TWzNZs&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e656a751\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uhpX9TWzNZs</a><br />\n搵唔到電視播版本 不過真係好快手轉咗個look 之後唱首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有，五少係香港人嚟 上節目教泰國人講「我唔要雲吞麵，我要食男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<a href=\"https://youtu.be/T3DHrzBYImY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT3DHrzBYImY&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4d5a3f76\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T3DHrzBYImY</a><br />\n<br />\n講翻泰劇，我睇嗰啲都好大路 害羞的女孩、三面娜迦、毒愛⋯⋯<br />\n除咗追開嗰啲，之後諗住睇 戀上黑澁會 風味絕配 <br />\n<br />\n身邊都無乜人睇泰劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 癡心妄想下希望連登搵到同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家一齊討論下"},{"pid":"674cbc91153ddef43dc6accfa30b22008770e107","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T20:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhi 巴 依排睇緊邊套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e1a5186dfba9e7eaa4bccf087f880b5a1a5f72","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T22:51:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚推一推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9866e9b66ddb58653968b5c688c3ec15d5ff0b0","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T22:52:22.000Z","msg":"我覺得我啲frds睇到呢個post都應該估到係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56acc82af09d4739b7cffa9e97d920991e2c0f4e","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T22:54:25.000Z","msg":"當初為咗靚仔，所以睇water boyy<br />\n真係好正 Earth<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好靚仔<br />\n連啲唔睇開泰劇bl既frd都忍唔住follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4dc7d83f1a893c81f8fa0b634a41b5359cce6d","tid":240970,"uid":17063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T00:03:22.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"aa6958970472f1dfe1ceed65f857a53670be69ef","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕輕一推</blockquote><br />\n你好 巴打 呢排睇緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc796fa74680c5532d99fc129f7693b660140b05","tid":240970,"uid":9684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:35:35.000Z","msg":"毒撚推pos